creator: UPS
descriptionHtml:
You’re busy, so let UPS help you easily manage shipments, track parcels, find UPS locations and much more with the UPS Mobile app. Download the UPS Mobile app to:

Track

- Find and follow your deliveries in transit
- Update your delivery location or change your delivery date
- Get delivery alerts to know when your parcel will arrive

Ship

- Estimate shipping costs and delivery times
- Take parcel dimensions with our in-app measurement tool
- Create a shipment and get shipping labels

Find the nearest UPS location to pack, send or collect your shipments
descriptionShort: The UPS Mobile app goes where you go so you can easily manage shipments.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
At UPS, we use your feedback to enhance the performance of the app. New features and improvements include:

- Biometric login remains active until user manually logs out
- Landscape mode re-enabled for tablet devices
- Ongoing enhancements to accessibility functionality
- General performance and bug fixes
